name: Going Roag
body:
### Dear Family and Friends,

## We can't wait to have you join us to celebrate our wedding in May!  

Click around to get the wedding schedule, list of places to stay, and activities on the agenda!  Let us know if you have any questions or need help making your travel plans. 

See you soon!
  
### Amelia and Nathaniel
